high_descs: Take the fruit in the fridge
Move to fruit near the oven
Open the oven put it to the fruit set the temperature and take it again
Place the fruit on the fridge
anns.task_desc: Take the fruit in the table put the fruit in oven place the fruit on the fridge

high_descs: Walk straight and turn towards right to reach the fridge
Open the fridge and take a mango from it and close the fridge
Turn back and walk straight and reach the microwave oven on the right side
Open the oven and put a mango inside of it and close the oven. After few seconds open the oven and take the mango out and close the oven again
Turn right and walk straight to reach the fridge
Open the fridge and put the mango inside and close the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put the mango in the fridge

high_descs: Go straight ahead and stop at the fridge on the right.
Pick up the mango from inside the fridge.
Go to the microwave opposite the fridge.
Use the microwave on the mango and pick it back up.
Put the mango back in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved mango in a fridge.
